name: Decorated Christmas Tree Cake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 box Betty Crocker vanilla cake mix
Tray or piece of cardboard covered with foil
1 drop Queen green gel food colour
Dr. Oetker Edible Decorations Giant Chocolate Stars

recipeInstructions.text: Press candy cane pieces in end of tree to make trunk. Roll out yellow ready to roll icing and using a small star cookie cutter, cut out a star. Place star on top of the tree. Store loosely covered at room temperature.
